abstract: |
  An exploration of explicit and implicit bias-reduced maximum likelihood estimation for structural equation models (SEMs) and latent growth curve models (LGCMs) is presented. Comparisons to prior work on resampling-based methods like Bootstrap and Jackknife are made. Performance of our methods are favourable.
keywords:
  - Structural Equation Models
  - Growth Curve Models
  - Bias Reduction
